Altitude to Zoom Level
https://gis.stackexchange.com/questions/12991/how-to-calculate-distance-to-ground-of-all-18-osm-zoom-levels
https://gis.stackexchange.com/questions/225794/converting-miles-above-ground-to-zoom-level

FOV = 45
A = 250 mi = 402336 m
n = 1105 / 2 = 552.5
R = A/n * tan(FOV)
  = 402336 / 552.5 * tan(45/180*pi) = 728.2 m/px ~ zoom = 7.75

ISS altitude, 250 miles

