gdalwarp -s_srs EPSG:4326 -t_srs EPSG:3857 -r bilinear -te -20037508.34 -20037508.34 20037508.34 20037508.34 dnb_land_ocean_ice.2012.54000x27000_geo.tif viirs_night_lights_2015_mercator_54000x27000.tif
gdalwarp -s_srs EPSG:4326 -t_srs EPSG:3857 -r bilinear -te -20037508.34 -20037508.34 20037508.34 20037508.34 dnb_land_ocean_ice.2012.13500x6750_geo.tif viirs_night_lights_2015_mercator_13500x6750.tif

### PROCESS

* Download cupola image from twitter post!
https://twitter.com/archillect/status/975441719520120837

* Use GIMP magic scissors to cut out transparent windows

* Download VIIRS Night Light 2015 geotiff data set
https://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/NaturalHazards/view.php?id=79765

* Reproject to Web Mercator using gdalwarp
https://tilemill-project.github.io/tilemill/docs/guides/reprojecting-geotiff/

* Create new map style and upload reprojected geotiff to Mapbox Studio
https://www.mapbox.com/help/uploads/

* Get map style ID 

5 